cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with tracking the pose of an object being manipulated by a robot hand, which falls under the domain of robotics (cs.RO). The method proposed uses vision-based techniques (cs.CV) and optimization algorithms (cs.AI) to improve the accuracy of the tracking. The use of physics simulation as a forward model also involves system dynamics (cs.SY). Finally, the use of GPU acceleration and parallel computing is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG).
